text: Alice blue is a whiteish shade of blue and a pale tone of azure blue. == Color codes == * Alice blue's color code is #F0F8FF * Alice blue is made of 94.1% red, 97.3% green and 100% blue * In CMYK color space, Alice blue is made of 5.9% cyan, 2.7% magenta, 0% yellow and 0% black. * It has 208 degrees, a saturation of 100% and a lightness of 97.1%. * It could be obtained by mixing #ffffff with #e1f1ff * Its closest web safe color is white
title: Alice blue
